phrs.translation: [机械]铣刀；铣制刀具（等于milling machine）
数控铣床；数值控制铣床

sentences.sentence: Leiwest Pak has machining centers, CNC millings, CNC lathes, automatic welding machines and other advanced processing equipment. So we can ensure high-quality, fast, stable supply of spare parts.
sentences.translation: 利慧包装拥有加工中心、数控铣床、数控车床、自动焊接机等先进的加工设备，同时全部选用国内外最优质的材料进行零件制造，因此得以确保优质、快速、稳定的零备件供应。

sentences.sentence: The effects of parameters on the amount and quality of laser milling were discussed. Moreover, various laser millings on horniness alloy were realized by the use of the optimized or composite arts.
sentences.translation: 分析了工艺参数对铣削量和铣削质量的影响，并利用优化或复合的工艺对硬质合金试样进行多样激光铣削。
